        "I have not conquered any planets, just a moon." Magmatron stated. 
"Bazooka speaks of me with respect because I rescued him from the scrap heap 
a few years ago." Magmatron was going to like trying to convert Phobia to his 
side. "Do you know where you are? Just asking because many do not."
